  "body": "### Component\r\n\r\nForge\r\n\r\n### Describe the feature you would like\r\n\r\nAs discussed in https://github.com/foundry-rs/foundry/issues/1961, it would be helpful to have a `--ignore` flag to the `forge coverage` command, so that we can avoid generating a coverage report for the test contracts.\r\n\r\nIdeally, the flag would be a glob, so that multiple directories and files can be excluded.",
